<br />
<strong>Supervisor Information:</strong></span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Email: <strong>{{{Supervisor_User__c.Email}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Mobile Number: <strong>{{{Supervisor_User__c.Phone}}}&nbsp;</strong></span></span></li>
